{
  "stem": "812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And I think that's one of the reasons that I can talk about it as easily-- not that it is easy to talk about.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "It-- it's always-- it never gets better.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "I speak frequently about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "I have spoken since 1979 at schools and organizations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And it is never easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And it's-- it's-- well, it just seems to me as though it's a very bad dream, as though it was a nightmare, as though it happened to somebody else, as though it never really happened to me.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And-- and that's how I rationalize, and that's how I can relate and I can talk about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "We were liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "We're forever grateful to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "I know that we're not always in good terms with that part of the world.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "But if it weren't for the Russians, we would definitely not be here today.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "In their crude way, they helped us along while we were in this little village.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "We took over the houses in Trobitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "The inhabitants, they left and fled.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "We took over their kitchens and their homes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And we ate of their unfamiliar nourishment-- the foods, the different meats and breads and butter and vegetables and whatnot and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "It was a very unfamiliar nourishment for our starved bodies, and certainly didn't agree with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "We became [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] continuously ill with dysentery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "And with-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we just couldn't tolerate all that unfamiliar nourishment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "Many, many people died in Trobitz, again, from malnutrition and typhoid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And of course, many people recovered and did very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "It was my father who had to die, six weeks after we were liberated, of typhoid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And this was after six years of ridicule and torment and heartache and horror.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
